   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>As per <a href="https://openhatch.org/wiki/Monitoring">https://openhatch.org/wiki/Monitoring</a> , I'm submitting the 
"monitor_hudson" branch for review.

This branch:

* Adds vm3.openhatch.org as a host

* Adds it as a server that needs HTTP and SSH monitoring

This, combined with my changes to vm3.openhatch.org to have Hudson be available 
on port 80, should cause Hudson to be quite effectively monitored.

Thanks!</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
